<span id="freeTextContainer7201516723134283351">Something about Tom Wolfe&apos;s prose (rest his soul) is so unfriendly yet so inviting, so dry yet so wry, so pedantic yet so accessible. It&apos;s indescribable. It&apos;d be easier to say that Tom simply had The Right Stuff.</span>
  <span id="freeText7201516723134283351" style="display:none">Something about Tom Wolfe's prose (rest his soul) is so unfriendly yet so inviting, so dry yet so wry, so pedantic yet so accessible. It's indescribable. It'd be easier to say that Tom simply had The Right Stuff.</span>
